parameterdescription.Ay: Reduced section area for XY-shear deformation calculations - when shear force influence along Y axis is taken into consideration
parameterdescription.Az: Reduced section area for XZ-shear deformation calculations - when shear force influence along Z axis is taken into consideration
parameterdescription.Iy: Moment of inertia about the Y axis
parameterdescription.Iz: Moment of inertia about the Z axis
parameterdescription.Wply: Plastic section modulus about Y axis
parameterdescription.Wplz: Plastic section modulus about Z axis
parameterdescription.Wtors: Section modulus for calculations of torsion stresses
parameterdescription.gamma: Rotation angle from local to principal coordinate system (maximum values of section moments of inertia)
parameterdescription.gap: Distance between chords in the complex sections
parameterdescription.vpy: Extreme fiber distance from the Z local axis of the point on the negative side of the Y axis
parameterdescription.vpz: Extreme fiber distance from the Y local axis of the point on the negative side of the Z axis
parameterdescription.vy: Extreme fiber distance from the Z local axis of the point on the positive side of the Y axis
